    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and has served as a dependable daily driver. While it remains mechanically sound and runs well, it shows typical signs of age and regular use. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some minor paint fading on the roof, and a few small door dings. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. All essential features like the heater and power windows are functional, though the air conditioning is not as cold as it once was. This is a solid, honest car for someone looking for reliable transportation without the premium price of a newer model.",
