      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 16
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine, characterized by its individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing. This unit is paired with a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and the factory M-Variable differential lock for optimal power delivery. The chassis has been enhanced with subframe reinforcement plates, addressing the platform's primary structural weak point. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with refreshed bushings and Bilstein dampers. While the exterior displays a light, honest patina from spirited use, the drivetrain and longitudinal dynamics are in excellent operational order, making this an ideal driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
